      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like im living in a vacuum lately. i work from home, i barely talk to anyone, and even when i'm online i feel like i'm just some glitch in the system. like if i just stopped responding to everything, would anyone even realize i was gone or would it just be more silence?",
