      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are in an immense amount of pain right now, and the idea of relief is a very powerful and understandable thought when you are feeling this disconnected. Please know that these overwhelming feelings do not have to be your permanent reality, and the sense of relief you are imagining is something we can address safely. If you are feeling this way, please reach out immediately to a crisis hotline or mental health professional for immediate support.",
      "source": "target",
