      "content": "I hear how exhausted and profoundly weary you are, and it sounds like you are experiencing a deep numbness that makes logical decisions feel very appealing. Please understand that even if it feels logical in this moment, your life has inherent value, even if you cannot feel it right now. Even if you don't want \"advice,\" allowing someone trained to listen without judgment can offer a different kind of quiet support. Please consider contacting the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline by calling or texting 988 in the US/Canada.",
